            "title": "Formation of high-order oligomers is required for functional bioactivity of an African bat henipavirus surface glycoprotein",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Laura",
                    "lastName": "Behner"
                },
                {
